<H4>    Velayati, Libya's al-Muntasir Meet </H4>

<F P=102> NC0206111494 Cairo MENA in Arabic 0958 GMT 2 Jun 94 </F>
<F P=103> NC0206111494 </F>
<F P=104>  Cairo MENA </F>
<F P=105>  Arabic </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] Cairo, 2 Jun (MENA) -- 'Umar al-Muntasir, Libyan 
secretary of the General People's Committee, met with Iranian 
Foreign Minister 'Ali Akbar Velayati today on the sidelines of 
the Non-Aligned Movement Conference currently being held in 
Cairo. 
  During the meeting, they discussed bilateral relations, 
coordinating their countries' stances at the conference, 
developments in Bosnia-Herzegovina, and restructuring the United 
Nations. 

</TEXT>

