  [Text] Cairo, 31 May (MENA) -- Yemeni Foreign Minister 
Muhammad Salim Basindwah met here this evening with Iranian 
Foreign Minister 'Ali Akbar Velayati on the sidelines of the 
Non-Aligned foreign ministers' meeting. The two ministers 
discussed the latest developments in Yemen and ways to reach a 
cease-fire and find a peaceful solution to the Yemeni crisis. 

