senior French Foreign Ministry official in a meeting held at 
Israel's Embassy in Paris. Our political correspondent 
'Imanu'el Rosen reports that Jerusalem is concerned by the 
increasing Palestinian pressure, exerted through foreign 
countries, for the achievement of a political status in 
Jerusalem. 

</TEXT>

