<H3> <TI>   No Stand Yet on `Worrisome' Italian Developments </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    No Stand Yet on `Worrisome' Italian Developments </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   TA0206100794 Jerusalem Qol Yisra'el in Hebrew 0900 GMT 2 Jun 
94 </F>

