<F P=100> ISRAEL </F>
<H3> <TI>   Trade Minister Harish To Hold Talks in Brussels </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Trade Minister Harish To Hold Talks in Brussels </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   TA3005111394 Jerusalem Qol Yisra'el in English 1000 GMT 30 
May 94 </F>

<F P=103> TA3005111394 </F>
<F P=104>  Jerusalem Qol Yisra'el </F>
