<H3> <TI>   New Yemeni Ambassador Arrives in Beirut </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    New Yemeni Ambassador Arrives in Beirut </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   NC0106194194 Beirut Radio Lebanon in Arabic 1900 GMT 1 Jun 94 </F>
<F P=103> NC0106194194 </F>
<F P=104>  Beirut Radio Lebanon </F>
<F P=105>  Arabic </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] Ahmad Muhammad al-Mutawakkil, the new Yemeni 
ambassador to Lebanon, arrived in Beirut this evening from Yemen 
via Amman. He was welcomed at the airport by Ambassador Ramiz 
Dimashqiyah, protocol director of the Foreign Ministry, and some 
staff members of the Yemeni embassy. The new Yemeni ambassador 
is expected to submit a copy of his credentials to Foreign 
Minister Faris Buwayz next week, and to submit his credentials 
to President Ilyas al-Hirawi at a later date. 

</TEXT>

