  [Text] An official spokesman has described the allegations 
against the president of Pakistan in a so-called fact sheet 
issued by Nawaz Muslim League as a forgery and a crude and 
disgraceful attempt to malign the head of state. The spokesman 
said the people of Pakistan were shocked by the wanton and 
irresponsible behavior of this defeated and discredited group of 
politicians to malign the head of state when he is abroad and is 
meeting world leaders. The spokesman said the callous attitude 
toward national interest is characteristic of this section of 
the opposition. 

