<F P=100> Palestinian Affairs </F>
<H3> <TI>   Qaddumi, Others Refuse To Enter Jericho </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Qaddumi, Others Refuse To Enter Jericho </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   NC0206142894 Jerusalem AL-NAHAR in Arabic 2 Jun 94 p 3 </F>
<F P=103> NC0206142894 </F>
<F P=104>  Jerusalem AL-NAHAR </F>
<F P=105>  Arabic </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] AL-NAHAR has learned from well-informed Palestinian 
sources that prominent members of the Fatah Central Committee 
have refused to return to Jericho. 
  During the committee's recent meeting, the members said they 
were not prepared to enter Jericho under the current 
circumstances. Only Intisar al-Wazir, alias Umm Jihad, and 
Salim al-Za'nun have agreed to enter Jericho. The Central 
Committee members who refused to return are Faruq Qaddumi; 
Mahmud 'Abbas, alias Abu Mazin, who signed the agreement; 'Abbas 
Zaki; Muhammad Jihad; Sakhr Habash; Muhammad Ghunaym; Hani 
al-Hasan; and Khalid al-Hasan. 

</TEXT>

