<H3> <TI>   Molotov Cocktails Hurled at Bethlehem Mayor's Home </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Molotov Cocktails Hurled at Bethlehem Mayor's Home </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   TA0306082794 Jerusalem Qol Yisra'el in English 0400 GMT 3 
Jun 94 </F>

<F P=103> TA0306082794 </F>
<F P=104>  Jerusalem Qol Yisra'el </F>
<F P=105>  English </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] Three Molotov cocktails were hurled last night at 
the home of Bethlehem mayor Ilyas Frayj, who is also a member of 
the Palestinian Autonomy Authority. The door to his home was 
slightly damaged, but no one was hurt. This is the second time 
in two weeks Frayj's home has been the target of a Molotov 
cocktail attack. 

</TEXT>

