<H3> <TI>   Security Forces Kill 4 `Terrorists' in Shoot-Out </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Security Forces Kill 4 `Terrorists' in Shoot-Out </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   NC0306190394 Cairo MENA in Arabic 1650 GMT 3 Jun 94 </F>
<F P=103> NC0306190394 </F>
<F P=104>  Cairo MENA </F>
<F P=105>  Arabic </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] Tama, Suhaj, 3 Jun (MENA)-- Four terrorists were 
killed in the area of Naj' Awlad Qasim in al-Hima village, Tama 
urban center in the governorate of Suhaj, early this morning. 
  A force of the State Security Detectives accompanied by the 
Central Security Forces of the Suhaj Security Directorate, 
surrounded the terrorists' hideout. The terrorists were killed 
in an exchange of fire with the force. 
  An officer and three soldiers from the force that stormed 
the 
terrorists' hideout were wounded during the exchange. 
  Officials from the Suhaj Security Directorate and the 
criminology laboratory went to the scene of the incident to 
inspect and the Prosecutor's office was told to launch an 
investigation. 

</TEXT>

