<F P=100> Morocco </F>
<H3> <TI>   King Discusses Peace Process With Israel's Peres </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    King Discusses Peace Process With Israel's Peres </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   LD0306153794 Rabat Moroccan Kingdom Radio Network in Arabic 
1300 GMT 3 Jun 94 </F>

<F P=103> LD0306153794 </F>
<F P=104>  Rabat Moroccan Kingdom Radio Network </F>
<F P=105>  Arabic </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] The Information Ministry has issued the following 
statement: 
  His Majesty King Hassan II, God make him victorious, 
received 
Israeli Foreign Minister Shim'on Peres at the royal court in 
Rabat on the evening of 2 June 1994. 
  During the meeting, Peres briefed the king on the stages of 
the peace process in the Middle East and his perceptions of the 
future and development of this process. On his part, the king 
reaffirmed to his guest Morocco's continued efforts to establish 
a just peace in the Middle East region. 
  Finally, his majesty the king confirmed to Peres that he has 
accepted an invitation to chair the international economic 
summit on the development of Middle Eastern countries which is 
scheduled to be held in Marrakech at the beginning of November. 

</TEXT>

