<H3> <TI>   Hamas Calls For More `Anti-Zionist' Operations </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Hamas Calls For More `Anti-Zionist' Operations </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   NC0606054094 Tehran Voice of the Islamic Republic of Iran 
First Program Network in Persian 0330 GMT 6 Jun 94 </F>

<F P=103> NC0606054094 </F>
<F P=104>  Tehran Voice of the Islamic Republic of Iran 
First Program Network </F>

<F P=105>  Persian </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] The Islamic Resistance Movement Hamas has stated 
that it will intensify its anti-Zionist operations. In a 
statement issued yesterday, Hamas once again condemned the 
accord between the PLO and the Zionist regime and called on its 
combatants to intensify their anti-Zionist operations. Hamas 
also called on the Palestinians in the occupied territories to 
go on a general strike on Thursday [9 June], the 79th month of 
the Palestinians' uprising. 

</TEXT>

