<H3> <TI>   Indian Troops Reportedly Kill 14 in Kashmir </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Indian Troops Reportedly Kill 14 in Kashmir </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   BK0406144694 Islamabad PTV Television Network in English 
1400 GMT 4 Jun 94 </F>

<F P=103> BK0406144694 </F>
<F P=104>  Islamabad PTV Television Network </F>
<F P=105>  English </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] In occupied Kashmir, Indian troops have martyred 
another 14 people during brutal operation. In Kupwara District 
alone, nine people were martyred by occupation forces. Indian 
soldiers rounded up more than 40 young Kashmiris during their 
siege and search operation and sent them to interrogation cells. 
In Srinagar, two bodies were recovered of people tortured to 
death during interrogation. Shiv Sena extremists in Kishtwar 
reportedly burned a Muslim woman to death. In Punch District, 
three people were killed in indiscriminate firing by Indian 
troops. In retaliation, mojahedin have stepped up their attacks 
on Indian military targets in the occupied valley. During these 
attacks many Indian soldiers were killed. 

</TEXT>

