  [Text] Amman--AL-RA'Y learns from well-informed sources 
that Palestinian President Yasir 'Arafat is expected in Amman 
tomorrow, Monday, for talks with His Majesty King Husayn and 
senior officials. 
  Sources say that discussions will center on effective joint 
