<H3> <TI>   Settler Wounded in Incident Near Hebron </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Settler Wounded in Incident Near Hebron </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   TA0206184994 Jerusalem Israel Television Channel 1 Network 
in Hebrew 1700 GMT 2 Jun 94 </F>

<F P=103> TA0206184994 </F>
<F P=104>  Jerusalem Israel Television Channel 1 Network 
in Hebrew 1700 GMT 2 Jun 94 </F>

<F P=105> Hebrew </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] A Qiryat Arba' resident sustained medium to serious 
wounds from stones were hurled at him at the Glass junction near 
Hebron. He was taken to Hadassah-'En Kerem Hospital and is 
undergoing an operation. Our correspondent Yoram Kohen reports 
that angry Qiryat Arba' inhabitants responded by stoning Arabs 
vehicles traveling along the Jerusalem-Hebron road. Nobody was 
hurt, but several cars were damaged. 

</TEXT>

