Arabic 2015 GMT 2 Jun 94 </F>

<F P=103> JN0206204494 </F>
<F P=104>  Damascus Syrian Arab Republic Radio Network </F>
<F P=105>  Arabic </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] His Excellency President Hafiz al-Asad yesterday 
received a telephone call from Yemeni Presidential Council 
Chairman 'Ali 'Abdallah Salih. 
  During the telephone conversation, the two presidents 
addressed the developments of the situation in Yemen. His 
excellency the president expressed Syria's regrets over the 
bloody course of events in Yemen, and reiterated the call to end 
the bloodshed in Yemen and reinstitute dialogue to resolve 
outstanding disputes in Yemen to safeguard unity. 
  His Excellency President Hafiz al-Asad today received a 
telephone call from 'Ali Salim al-Bid, secretary general of the 
Yemeni Socialist Party. During the telephone conversation, 
al-Bid informed his excellency the president of the developments 
in Yemen. His excellency the president expressed the sadness 
Syria feels because of the bloodshed and infighting in Yemen. 
He reiterated, on Syria's behalf, his call for an end to the 
fighting, and for a return to dialogue to resolve outstanding 
disputes within the framework of Yemeni unity. 

